  "title": "🤩IMMEDIATE HIRE🤩Junior Business Associate- international exposure/ training provided",
  "description": "<h3><strong>No experience?</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>No Worries! 🤗</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Seeking eager learners who thrive in fast-paced environments with amazing tons of perks for YOU! 🌟</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Not only you have a chance to work in a supportive environment, You can also make an impact and also be part of brainstorming ideas in the office🤝</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>There’s even more!!! The fun doesn’t stop there!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>•⁠ ⁠You can grow your network through Travel opportunities to meet like-minded individuals ✈️</p>\n<p>•⁠ ⁠Career plans for your progression and growth 📈</p>\n<p>•⁠ ⁠Gym membership to keep you in your mental agility🏋️‍♀️</p>\n<p>•⁠ ⁠Work-hard, play-hard vibes which is ideal for young pros like you 🎉</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>-Achieve sales targets and improve the sales of clients' company</p>\n<p>-Creating awareness about the products or services that our clients is providing</p>\n<p>-Leading a sales and marketing team and facilitating the team’s growth</p>\n<p>-Get involved in client’s marketing through business development</p>\n<p>-Develop analytical and problem-solving skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Ready to Learn! Grow! &amp; make meaningful impacts! We want you on our team now! Can’t wait to create something amazing together! ✨🔥</strong></h3>",
